The Kenyan shooting team performed exceptionally well in the just concluded southern national’s shooting competition, with expert shooter Sammy Onyango winning gold.it was a double win for master shooter Robert Nyamongo who bagged gold in international category and silver in e?sp category losing by 1 second to the gold winner. Others who bagged medals were Anthony Wahome who won a silver medal in E?S?P division, Peter Njoroge a silver medalist in c?c?p division sharpshooter and Mwangi Gikonyo who scooped bronze in the c?c?p division of marksman.